{
  "stem": "71.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we-- she got married.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And was a system in Poland that you had a seamstress come into the house and do the trousseau.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Well, the same way as my mother did for my sister, she did for her, too.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they opened a little store-- she and her husband opened a little store, because she saved up the money that she was paid for.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And when the war broke out, she was the one to bring things to us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She remembered the children-- well, she, she almost raised us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And if she could find something, till they closed the ghetto, she used to bring things in for us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But the time they closed the ghetto, there was no way of getting anything in.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I went back with my mother.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father tried to come but he was, a few times, sent back-- beaten up and sent back.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But somehow my-- there was a border, because Lodz belonged to Germany where Warsaw belonged to Poland, occupied by Germans.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, my mother somehow got through.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And going back, my mother-- [BACKGROUND NOISE] my-- Just tell-- so you went back with your mother to Lodz.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They, they were-- my family was already-- my father, mother, and my sisters-- in the ghetto already.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that-- a week later my sister Regina, who lives here, was diagnosed with typhoid fever, and she was taken to a hospital.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "At that time, we knew that somebody's taken to the hospital, she will never come back.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, I was running after, and I blamed myself that because I came to ghetto, she got sick.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But got, got-- we got help.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She came back from the hospital.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She recovered.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were together, and we worked in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
